import React from 'react'

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <FooterContainer>
      <FooterWrap>
          <SocialMedia>
              <SocialMediaWrap>
                <SocialLogo to="/">Pizza</SocialLogo>
                <SocialIcons>
                  <SocialIconLink>
                      
                  </SocialIconLink>
                </SocialIcons>
              </SocialMediaWrap>
          </SocialMedia>
      </FooterWrap>
    </FooterContainer>
  )
}

export default Footer
